					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Bregalad wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">True, but remember they had no mapper IRQs to work with !</div>
<br />Sure, but when designing a game you have to think of all the possibilities, how different aspects of it (specially the ones that involve hardware "tricks") will work with each other. You can't realize that the sound effects screw up the raster effects and just say "fuck it" and ignore this bug. IMO, visual glitches are the worst kind, and should be avoided at all costs.</div>

